                                     scmake

                                  EXPERIMENTAL

A simple build tool for C and other sorts of projects. Designed for POSIX
systems. It helps you write simple configure scripts and runs your Makefiles
through the C preprocessor. Check out the examples directory to get an idea of
how it works.

DEPENDENCIES

- sh
- make
- cpp

INSTALLATION

$ mkdir build && cd build
$ ../configure
$ make
# make install

Use ../configure --help to learn about available options.

MANUAL

scmake(7), scmake(5)
